            "title": "Climatic, geographic and anthropogenic factors shape the structure of bat–fruit networks in the Neotropical region",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Ana Beatriz",
                    "lastName": "Ligo"
                },
                {
